  ☆ノノハ
  从*’w’)
(つactorsと)

Evaluation of API and performance of different actor libraries (and lock-free queues)

Hardware required
-----------------
CPU: 2 cores or more
RAM: min 6Gb for 64-bit or 3Gb for 32-bit

Software installed required
---------------------------
JDK: 1.7.0_03 or newer
Maven: 3.0.4 or newer

Building & running benchmarks
-----------------------------
Use following command-line instructions for JDK 64-bit:
mvn -B clean install > outX.txt
For JDK 32-bit use the 32-bit profile:
mvn -B clean install -P 32-bit > outX.txt

Test result descriptions
------------------------
out1.txt
Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-2640M CPU @ 2.80GHz (max turbo 3.50GHz), RAM 12Gb DDR3-1333, Windows 7 sp1, JDK 1.7.0_03 64-bit

out2.txt (outdated)
2 x Intel(R) Xeon(R) Processor E5540 @ 2.53GHz, RAM 24Gb DDR2-1066, Ubuntu 11 Server edition, JDK 1.7.0_03 64-bit

out3.txt
Intel(R) Core(TM)2 Duo CPU E6850 @ 3.00GHz, RAM 4Gb, Windows 7, JDK 1.7.0_03 32-bit

out4.txt (outdated)
Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-2630QM @ 2.00GHz (max turbo 2.90GHz), RAM 8Gb DDR3-1600, Windows 7 sp1, JDK 1.7.0_03 64-bit